description:
GNOME 47 Alpha is now available for public testing with support for accent colors, Wayland improvements, and many other changes. Here's what to expect!

The post GNOME 47 Alpha Desktop Environment Released with Support for Accent Colors appeared first on 9to5Linux - do not reproduce this article without permission. This RSS feed is intended for readers, not scrapers.
title: GNOME 47 Alpha Desktop Environment Released with Support for Accent Colors
